<L>__{exterior barge later day}
<A>__{epps pulls herself onto the deck from below. she stands on a rusting 5000 ton tank barge being pulled in the open ocean by a brawny marine tug at the end of a 150 foot tow cable. it is a typical summer day in the southern bering sea, which means a healthy chop and a stiff cold breeze out of the north west. she closes the hatch behind her and makes her way forward.}
